PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-1338, which authorized the Minister of Finance to make loans of $2 million to the CANADIAN SALTFISH CORPORATION in the 1993/94 fiscal year, changing the aggregate balance outstanding for loans to accommodate the roll over of existing loans.
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-1338, which authorized the Minister
of Finance to make loans of $2 million to the CANADIAN SALTFISH
CORPORATION in the 1993/94 fiscal year, changing the aggregate balance
outstanding for loans to accommodate the roll over of existing loans.
